# Active per-install skills dir — populated from skills-template/ on first
# `flockbots init`. Gitignored so user customizations + kg build output
# (graph.json, graph.html, cache/, GRAPH_REPORT.md, etc.) don't block
# upgrades. The shipped defaults live in skills-template/ (tracked).
skills/

# Per-install scratchpad — deploy URLs, last-reconfigure time, kg build
# time. Lives at ~/.flockbots/state.json on a real install; ignored here
# so dogfooding from the source tree never commits one accidentally.
state.json
